rid",description:"A grid layout to showcase team members with images, roles, names, and descriptions.",type:"team",visualConfigPresets:[{showImages:!0},{showImages:!1}],exampleConfig:{kicker:"Meet the Team",heading:"Our Dedicated Professionals",description:"We are proud to introduce our team of dedicated professionals who are committed to delivering excellence in every project. Get to know the people behind our success.",buttons:[{label:"Contact Us",href:"#contact",actionType:"section"}],items:[{name:"Sarah Mitchell",role:"Chief Executive Officer",image:{src:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2?w=400&h=400&fit=crop",alt:"Sarah Mitchell"},description:"Sarah brings over 20 years of leadership experience and is passionate about driving innovation and growth across our organization."},{name:"Marcus Chen",role:"Chief Technology Officer",image:{src:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?w=400&h=400&fit=crop",alt:"Marcus Chen"},description:"Marcus leads our technology vision with expertise in AI, cloud architecture, and building scalable systems that power our platform."},{name:"Emily Rodriguez",role:"Head of Product Design",image:{src:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?w=400&h=400&fit=crop",alt:"Emily Rodriguez"},description:"Emily crafts beautiful, user-centered designs that transform complex problems into intuitive experiences our users love."},{name:"James Thompson",role:"Lead Software Engineer",image:{src:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?w=400&h=400&fit=crop",alt:"James Thompson"},description:"James architects and builds robust software solutions, leading our engineering team with a focus on code quality and innovation."},{name:"Priya Patel",role:"Director of Marketing",image:{src:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551836022-d5d88e9218df?w=400&h=400&fit=crop",alt:"Priya Patel"},description:"Priya develops data-driven marketing strategies that amplify our brand and 